<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge" />
    <title>Quick Quiz</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="app.css" />
</head>
<style>
    * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
        background-image: url("./image/qkey.jpg");
        background-color: #cccccc;
        height: 500px;
        background-position: center;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        background-size: cover;
    }

    .homepage {
        padding: 0;
        width: 10;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 15px;
        color: white;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;
        overflow: hidden;
        position: inherit;
        -webkit-text-emphasis: triangle;
        background-color: #e9e9e9;
        -webkit-appearance: button-bevel;
        -webkit-appearance: slider-horizontal;
        margin: initial;
        position: absolute;
        max-width: 1000px;
        margin: 0 auto;

    }

    .homepage a {
        float: left;
        display: block;
        color: black;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 14px 16px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 17px;
    }

    .homepage a:hover {
        background-color: white;
        color: black;
    }

    .homepage a.active {
        background-color: #2196F3;
        color: white;
    }


    @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {}

    .homepage a,
    .homepage input[type=text] {

        display: block;
        text-align: center;
        float: left;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 16px;
    }

    .homepage input[type=text] {
        border: 1px solid #ccc;
    }

    .green {
        background-color: lawngreen;
    }

    .register {
        background-color: lightcoral;
    }

    .question {
        background-color: lightgreen;
    }

    .login {
        background-color: lightgray;
    }

    .creat {
        background-color: gray;
    }

    .img {
        text-align-last: end;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        position: sticky;
        text-align-last: end;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        display: flow-root;
        padding: 0px;
        -webkit-appearance: checkbox;
        border-bottom: dotted;
        -webkit-margin-before-collapse: discard;
        position: unset;
        mix-blend-mode: color-burn;
    }

    .p {
        color: blue;
    }

    .home {
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 0;
        background: rgb(0, 0, 0);
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
        color: #f1f1f1;
        width: 99%;
        padding: 0px;
        font-size: unset;
        margin: 0px 0px 0px -7px;
    }

    h1 {
        color: hsla(hue, saturation, lightness, alpha)
    }

    div.transbox {
        margin: 30px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border: 1px solid black;
        opacity: 0.6;
        filter: alpha(opacity=60);
    }

    div.transbox p,
    h1,
    h3 {
        margin: 0%;
        padding: 2px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #000000;
    }

    div.quizpix {
        margin: 0px 0px 0px 900px;
        opacity: 0.5;
        filter: alpha(opacity=100);
        border: none;
        max-width: 1000;
        align-items: center;
        position: absolute;
    }
</style>

<body>
    <div>
        <div class="homepage">
            <a class="active" href="#home">Home</a>
            <a class="Creat" href="createQuestions" > Set Question </a>
            <a class="register" href="register" disabled="disabled">Registration</a>
            <a class="login" href="login">Login</a>
            <a class="green" href="getResult">View Result</a>
            <a class="question" href="questions">Start Quiz</a>
        </div>
        <div class="home">
            <div class="transbox">
                <h1>Hard Work Pays!!!</h1>
                <h3> We are still learning </h3>
                <p> Perfect is the enemy of good.” <br>
                    “Be curious, not judgmental.”<br>
                    “Learning is not attained by chance. <br>
                    "It must be sought for with ardor and attended to with
                    diligence.” <br>
                    “CHANGE IS THE END RESULT OF ALL TRUE LEARNING </p>

            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="quizpix">
            <div>
                <img src="/image/qword.png">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>